2013 Rules
==========

[<img class="left" src="/resources/2013/rulebook.jpg" />](/resources/2013/rulebook.pdf)
The rules, regulations and specifications for the SR 2013 competition can be found in the [rulebook](/resources/2013/rulebook.pdf).
The PDF may be subject to minor changes, so please ensure you're using the most up-to-date version.
We will also let you know of any important changes by email.
